title: Doctor Who Original Complete (1963-1989)
description:
This is all the original Dr. Who episodes from 1963-1989, along with some DVD bonus documentaries.  Whereas other torrents have each episode separate, I have merged all episodes of each serial into a single mp4 file.  I have prioritized smaller size over higher quality, though some files are still very large.  I used freeware AVC (Any Video Converter) to merge these files.

Some Dr Who episodes were lost by the BBC.  They have provided reconstructed episodes from stage pictures.  I have created split-screen versions, using these stage pictures combined with fan-created animations.  I used freeware VSDC to create these versions
